data.description: Absolutely adorable! This home has been well maintained and is in a great area on the west side of Beloit. The home has been recently renovated, with new floors, new kitchen with lots of cabinet space, and a small deck. Nice size one car garage with a spacious backyard. This home will be perfect for a single person or if you're looking to downsize. Don't miss out on this one!
